name: Frog Robot Print
description:
This is the limited edition print I created with my Jan 2013 Kickstarter campaign.

This is a fancy limited edition print of my original acrylic painting "Robot" on Hahnemuhle German Etching paper. The original was a detailed painting on wood board depicting a frog holding his favorite robot and announcing "Robot", you see, because "Robot" sounds like "Ribbit".

The print is 6 inches square and was produced as a limited edition of 70. Each print is signed and numbered and comes with two free stickers.

http://www.kickstarter.com/projects/2101475072/jennifer-lewis-illustration-limited-edition-frog-r
